Short:    AGA/HD fix for World of Wonders "Crazy Cars 2" Cracktro
Author:   S.Pucino@gmx.de (Max Headroom/TEX)
Uploader: S.Pucino@gmx.de (Max Headroom/TEX)
Version:  1.1
Type:     demo/intro
Requires: demo/ecs/wow_crak.lha, WHDLoad v14.x+

This patch applies to Crazy Cars 2 Crack-Intro, ©World of Wonders

This intro was rather easy to patch. I'm getting better ;-))

REQUIREMENTS:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 - WHDLoad V14+
 - Intro req. 0.5 MB ChipMem
 - Barfly or ASM-One for compilation. I prefer ASM-One for smaller code ^_^
 - The intro itself ;) Download it under...: Aminet: demo/ecs/wow_crak.lha

FEATURES:
~~~~~~~~~
 - Replaced empty DBRA-Loop in SoundTracker-player
 - Nice OS3.5 Icon included.
 - Complete and fully commented source-code included!

HISTORY:
~~~~~~~~
 1.1 (2024-08-14) by Wepl
 - made 68000 compatible (_resload at odd address)
 - removed OSEmu usage
 - added keyboard quit
 - tested on 68060/50
 - source: https://github.com/wepl/winstalls/tree/master/ctros/

CAVEATS:
~~~~~~~~
 - Tested ONLY on my A1230/50 MHz (2MB Chip, 16MB Fast).
   Sorry, no more hardware at home.  ^_^
 - I'm a BEGINNER ! Please don't expect something like an assembler-crack
   who gives you a PPC-native slave ;)

